data.description: Like new condition now available in the Red Fox Meadows Subdivision of East Helena. The master planned community features curbing and asphalt streets throughout, community sewer with private wells, storage unit facility, and close proximity to local schools and recreation on nearby lakes. This contemporary build style features single level/zero stair entry, an oversized foyer entry, inviting fireplace, covered concrete back patio, and generous kitchen island to gather and prepare. Upgraded finishes include barn doors in the primary bedroom with spacious walk-in closet system, tiled walk-in shower, and sizeable laundry. Amenities include custom cabinetry and trim work, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and luxury waterproof flooring in main living areas. Including a three car garage with epoxy finish, covered concrete pack patio, additional parking, u/g sprinklers, and partial vinyl fencing. Call Heather Lay at (406) 431-1571 or your real estate professional. OPD Updated after Inspection. See attached Report pages and Addendum.
